title=\"Stanford University Estimated Tuition and Fees for 2024 \u2013 2024 Session\">Stanford University Estimated Tuition and Fees for 2024 \u2013 2024 Session<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-apply-stanford-university\/#Stanford_University_Acceptance_Rate\" title=\"Stanford University Acceptance Rate\">Stanford University Acceptance Rate<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-apply-stanford-university\/#How_to_Apply_Stanford_University\" title=\"How to Apply | Stanford University\">How to Apply | Stanford University<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-apply-stanford-university\/#Check_Application_Status_Stanford_University\" title=\"Check Application Status | Stanford University\">Check Application Status | Stanford University<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h2 id=\"university-location\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"University_Location\"><\/span>University Location<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<table class=\"table borderless\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Address<\/th>\n<td>450 Serra Mall Stanford<br \/>\n94305\u00a0California<br \/>\nUnited States<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Tel<\/th>\n<td>+1 (650) 723 2300<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Fax<\/th>\n<td>+1 (650) 725 6847<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other locations<\/th>\n<td>Washington, New York, Monterey<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans', arial, sans-serif; font-size: 27px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\"><br \/>\nPrograms and Accreditation | Stanford University<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Stanford University (SU) offers courses and programs leading to officially recognized higher education degrees, such as bachelor&#8217;s degrees, master&#8217;s degrees, and doctorate degrees in several areas of study. International students are welcome to apply for enrollment.<\/p>\n<p class=\"text-justify\">SU also provides students with several academic and non-academic facilities and services, including a library, housing, sports facilities, financial aid and\/or scholarships, study abroad and exchange programs, online courses, distance learning opportunities, and administrative services.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h2 id=\"\"><\/h2>\n<h2 id=\"stanford-university-requirements-and-deadlines\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Stanford_University_Requirements_and_Deadlines\"><\/span>Stanford University Requirements and Deadlines<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>You are interested in the Standard University Admission requirements and deadlines. Stanford University requires the following as criteria for admission<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"required-application-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_Application_Documents\"><\/span>Required Application Documents<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Common Application<\/li>\n<li>$90 nonrefundable application fee\u00a0or\u00a0fee waiver request<\/li>\n<li>ACT or SAT scores (test optional for 2024\u201325; refer to testing for score reporting policies)<\/li>\n<li>School Report form and counselor letter of recommendation<\/li>\n<li>Official transcript(s) or academic results<\/li>\n<li>Letters of recommendation from two teachers<\/li>\n<li>Midyear transcript (by February 15)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Application and Testing Deadlines<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Submit all documents and applications on or before the deadline. Follow the chat below to know your deadline.<\/p>\n<table style=\"height: 496px;\" width=\"636\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\"><\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\"><strong>Restrictive Early Action<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\"><strong>Regular Decision<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\">Application with Arts Portfolio<\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\">October 15<\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\">December 5<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\">Materials for Arts Portfolio<\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\">October 20<\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\">December 10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\"><strong>Standard Application Deadline<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\"><strong>November 1<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\"><strong>January 5<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\">Notification of Missing Documents<\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\">Mid-November<\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\">Mid-February<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\"><strong>Decision Released By<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\"><strong>December 15<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\"><strong>April 1<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"39%\">Student Reply Date<\/td>\n<td width=\"34%\">May 1<\/td>\n<td width=\"26%\">May 1<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2 id=\"stanford-university-estimated-tuition-and-fees-for-2024-2024-session\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Stanford_University_Estimated_Tuition_and_Fees_for_2024_%E2%80%93_2024_Session\"><\/span>Stanford University Estimated Tuition and Fees for 2024 \u2013 2024 Session<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Full-time enrollment:\u00a0 <\/strong>$19,231 per quarter (full-time enrollment is 12-20 units per quarter)<\/p>\n<p><strong>Summer only: <\/strong>\u00a0$1,282 per unit (units fewer than 12)<\/p>\n<p>For more details, visit https:\/\/studentservices.stanford.edu\/my-finances\/tuition-fees<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"stanford-university-acceptance-rate\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Stanford_University_Acceptance_Rate\"><\/span>Stanford University Acceptance Rate<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The acceptance rate for Stanford University is 5.2% off the payments<a href=\"http:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">.<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-stanford-university\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_Stanford_University\"><\/span>How to Apply | Stanford University<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To apply for admission to Stanford University, kindly follow the steps below;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.commonapp.org\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Common Application App<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Mouse on the start Application<\/li>\n<li>Fill in all required fields<\/li>\n<li>Pay all application fees<\/li>\n<li>Submit relevant documents<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"check-application-status-stanford-university\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Check_Application_Status_Stanford_University\"><\/span>Check Application Status | Stanford University<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Login to the Common Application portal<\/li>\n<li>Click the Check Admission Status<\/li>\n<li>Accept Admission Offers<\/li>\n<li>pay Acceptance Deposit<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"panel-heading\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Stanford University Undergraduate Application is available online. Prospective candidates can apply through the Common Application App. The standard&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":18333,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[956],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8470"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8470"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2